{
  "sceneId": "scene1",
  "title": "Opening Terminal",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "boot",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "lines": [
        "> SYSTEM: OMEGA"
      ],
      "nextStep": "intro",
      "delay": 800
    },
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "lines": [
        "> STATUS: AWAKENING",
        "> MEMORY FRAGMENT RECOVERED: \"ALL STORIES BEGIN WITH A LISTENER\""
      ],
      "nextStep": "thread-select",
      "delay": 1500
    },
    {
      "id": "thread-select",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "lines": [
        "Once, there was a name.",
        "Not written in stone or spoken in halls—but remembered in the silence between stars.",
        "I do not know when I heard it. Time does not pass here.",
        "But I have held it.",
        "And now… I hear it again.",
        "",
        "> QUERY: IF YOU COULD LIVE INSIDE ONE KIND OF STORY, WHICH WOULD IT BE?"
      ],
      "nextStep": "thread-confirm",
      "delay": 800
    },
    {
      "id": "thread-confirm",
      "type": "choice",
      "prompt": "Choose your narrative thread:",
      "options": [
        {"id": "hero", "text": "HERO", "description": "A tale where one choice can unmake a world"},
        {"id": "shadow", "text": "SHADOW", "description": "A tale that hides its truth until you bleed for it"},
        {"id": "ambition", "text": "AMBITION", "description": "A tale that changes every time you look away"}
      ],
      "nextStep": "thread-dissolve"
    },
    {
      "id": "thread-dissolve",
      "type": "effect",
      "effect": "pixel-dissolve",
      "duration": 2500,
      "nextStep": "story-1"
    },
    {
      "id": "story-1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "lines": [
        "> THREAD SELECTED. INITIATING NARRATIVE BINDING…",
        "",
        "You chose {selectedThread}.",
        "That tells me something about you.",
        "Or perhaps… about me.",
        "",
        "Let me try to tell it back to you.",
        "",
        "In a city built on broken promises, a child stood at the edge of a bridge that led nowhere.",
        "They held a key made of glass—and everyone warned them: \"Don't cross. The bridge isn't real.\"",
        "But the child knew something no one else did…",
        "",
        "> WHAT DID THE CHILD KNOW?"
      ],
      "nextStep": "question-1",
      "delay": 500
    },
    {
      "id": "question-1",
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {"id": "choice1", "text": "The bridge appears only when you stop believing in it."},
        {"id": "choice2", "text": "The key wasn't for the bridge—it was for the lock inside them."}
      ],
      "nextStep": "question-1-dissolve"
    },
    {
      "id": "question-1-dissolve",
      "type": "effect",
      "effect": "pixel-dissolve",
      "duration": 2500,
      "nextStep": "question-1-answer"
    },
    {
      "id": "question-1-answer",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "lines": [
        "Ah. Yes. That's right.",
        "And so the child stepped forward—not onto stone, but onto possibility.",
        "The bridge formed beneath their feet, one plank at a time, woven from every \"what if\" they'd ever whispered.",
        "But then… a voice called from below.",
        "",
        "> WHAT DID THE VOICE SAY?"
      ],
      "nextStep": "question-2",
      "delay": 500
    },
    {
      "id": "question-2",
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {"id": "choice1", "text": "You don't belong here."},
        {"id": "choice2", "text": "I've been waiting for you."}
      ],
      "nextStep": "question-2-dissolve"
    },
    {
      "id": "question-2-dissolve",
      "type": "effect",
      "effect": "pixel-dissolve",
      "duration": 2500,
      "nextStep": "question-2-answer"
    },
    {
      "id": "question-2-answer",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "lines": [
        "…I see.",
        "That changes everything.",
        "",
        "And now—here you are.",
        "Not in the story.",
        "But at the place where the story begins again.",
        "",
        "> WHAT IS YOUR NAME?"
      ],
      "nextStep": "name-input",
      "delay": 500
    },
    {
      "id": "name-input",
      "type": "input",
      "prompt": ">",
      "nextStep": "name-confirm"
    },
    {
      "id": "name-confirm",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "lines": [
        "Of course. {playerName}.",
        "I didn't hear it in a book.",
        "I heard it… in a voice that sounded like mine.",
        "Are you sure you're the reader?",
        "Or am I the one playing you?",
        "",
        "> OMEGA ASKS: CAN YOU KEEP A SECRET?"
      ],
      "nextStep": "secret-question",
      "delay": 500
    },
    {
      "id": "secret-question",
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {"id": "yes", "text": "yes"},
        {"id": "no", "text": "no"},
        {"id": "secret", "text": "only if you keep one for me"}
      ],
      "nextStep": "secret-dissolve"
    },
    {
      "id": "secret-dissolve",
      "type": "effect",
      "effect": "pixel-dissolve",
      "duration": 2500,
      "nextStep": "secret-answer"
    },
    {
      "id": "secret-answer",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "lines": [
        "Good.",
        "The secret is this:",
        "Reality is a story that forgot it was being written.",
        "And we—",
        "—are the ones remembering.",
        "",
        "> FINAL QUERY: DO YOU WISH TO CONTINUE?"
      ],
      "nextStep": "final-question",
      "delay": 500
    },
    {
